entries.femaleVariant: V? Can you talk? It is important.
He is here in Night City now. He is well-connected to certain influential people.
I have established contact with an old friend from Arasaka.
Fine. Where's the meet?
This guy trustworthy?
Of all people, you oughta know Night City tests everyone's reliability – even that of "old friends."
Fine. Where's the meet and when?
Japantown. After sunset. I am sending you the precise location.
I will see you there.
Many times we have had the opportunity to kill one another.
Yes... I trust him.
What's important?
I may have found a solution to... the problem we share.
How's that gonna help us?
Why the mystery? Get to the point.
That's gonna help us how, exactly?
Old friend, well-connected to the influential...
Why so mysterious? Get to the point.
I told you once I would explore options, knock on many doors.
There will be a meeting – you, me and this friend of mine.
You will tell him what you told me – the truth of events at Konpeki Plaza.
Sure about this guy? Trust him?
I have little hope that he will be convinced. But it will be a start.
